#                        people of the same nationality must sit next to each other?
# litex_code: this file
# proof_attempt: Start from labeled permutations. Identify the internal swaps that do not
#                change the visible outcome. Use quotient counting by repeated classes.
#                Evaluate n! divided by the product of repeated-class factorials.
